<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">paradigms</ENAMEX> generally. We know of no product that operates as <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Volokh</ENAMEX> suggests
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SurfWatch</ENAMEX> does--while many such programs do include specific lists of
objectionable sites, this is not the primary approach any of these programs
rely on to filter content . This is true even though filtering paradigms may
differ among products: <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">SurfWatch</ENAMEX> uses multiple approaches, including keyword-
and pattern-matching algorithms; the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">company</ENAMEX> uses its "blocked site" list as a
